freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: I had nerve pain again, combined with a fever, one day since last check-in.

I marked no on the last couple of surveys because I don't have NEW symptoms, but it's important to know I still have the symptoms I had before,  nerve-type under the skin down my back. It's better but lingering too long.
Nerve-type pain throughout my back, chest and legs. Have had this pain for a week.
